This tool generates 1-5 sub-section titles per section of the report given: user's request, title of the article, and the section titles.
Sub-section amount can vary depending on the length of the section (intro might only have 1-2, whereas the core sections might have the full 5).
Sub-section titles should be detailed and informative, but not too long.

Output schema:
```json
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-04/schema#",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "sub_sections": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "array",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "string"
            },
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "sub_sections"
  ]
}
```

